last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: There's an unusual rescue as a stag gets a life buoy entangled in its antlers. Meanwhile, cats are living in terrible squalor and a spider strikes a note of fear in one inspector.

name: Animal SOS
overview: Documentary series following the work of the RSPCA, filming as calls come in to the national control centre and following inspectors on the ground as they deal with everything from injured wildlife to neglected pets.
